library(manCULTA)

set.seed(seed)
taskid <- 1
data <- GenData(taskid = taskid)
summary(as.matrix(data))

Model Fitting 

fit <- FitCULTA2Profiles(
  data = data,
  wd = ".",
  ncores = parallel::detectCores(),
  mplus_bin = "mplus",
  starts = c(1000, 500),
  stiterations = 200,
  stscale = 2
)
summary(fit)
